<TITLE>Why I snubbed Barcelona move  Coutinho</TITLE>


<TEXT>
Liverpool playmaker, Philippe Coutinho, has <EVENT eid="e1" class="I_ACTION">revealed</EVENT> that he <EVENT eid="e2" class="OCCURRENCE">snubbed</EVENT> a <EVENT eid="e3" class="OCCURRENCE">move</EVENT> to Barcelona to <EVENT eid="e4" class="OCCURRENCE">sign</EVENT> a new <TIMEX3 tid="t1" type="DURATION" value="P5Y">five-year</TIMEX3> deal at Anfield , because he can <EVENT eid="e5" class="PERCEPTION">see</EVENT> the ambition of the club. 
 
The 24-year-old Brazilian was a target for the La Liga chmpions, but has <TIMEX3 tid="t2" type="DATE" value="PRESENT_REF">now</TIMEX3> <EVENT eid="e6" class="OCCURRENCE">pledged</EVENT> his future to the Reds, with a contract that <EVENT eid="e7" class="OCCURRENCE">makes</EVENT> him the clubs highest earner at 150,000 per <TIMEX3 tid="t3" type="DURATION" value="P1W">week</TIMEX3>. 
 
Coutinho <EVENT eid="e8" class="REPORTING">told</EVENT> Daily Mail he had no second thoughts, as soon as he was <EVENT eid="e9" class="OCCURRENCE">offered</EVENT> fresh terms. 
 
No need to <EVENT eid="e10" class="OCCURRENCE">wait</EVENT>. I know. I <EVENT eid="e11" class="I_STATE">live</EVENT> this every <TIMEX3 tid="t4" type="DURATION" value="PXD">day</TIMEX3>, I can <EVENT eid="e12" class="OCCURRENCE">smell</EVENT> it. I <EVENT eid="e13" class="I_STATE">see</EVENT> the ambition of the club, my teammates, the manager. I am <EVENT eid="e14" class="OCCURRENCE">living</EVENT> it, <EVENT eid="e15" class="I_ACTION">seeing</EVENT> it. Wait to <EVENT eid="e16" class="OCCURRENCE">sign</EVENT>? No. No. Now is the right time, he <EVENT eid="e17" class="REPORTING">said</EVENT>. 
 
I <EVENT eid="e18" class="I_STATE">understand</EVENT> what Liverpool <EVENT eid="e19" class="OCCURRENCE">means</EVENT>. We can <EVENT eid="e20" class="REPORTING">say</EVENT> [Kenny] Dalglish, [Ian] Rush, [Alan] Hansen, [Graeme] Souness, [Luis] Suarez, [Steven] Gerrard. Ive been here quite <TIMEX3 tid="t5" type="DURATION" value="PXY">a few years</TIMEX3> already, its not like I am new. I understand. 
 
To have <EVENT eid="e21" class="OCCURRENCE">signed</EVENT> a new contract at this club, my goal is to be thought of <TIMEX3 tid="t6" type="DATE" value="FUTURE_REF">one day</TIMEX3> in the same way as these players. They are legends. You <EVENT eid="e22" class="I_STATE">define</EVENT> the success of a player by his loyalty or his titles. Or both. In order to be part of this group, I have so much to <EVENT eid="e23" class="OCCURRENCE">do</EVENT>. 
 
I <EVENT eid="e24" class="I_STATE">want</EVENT> to <EVENT eid="e25" class="OCCURRENCE">win</EVENT> titles. Five years is my new contract  it gives me that opportunity. 
 
Coutinho has <EVENT eid="e26" class="REPORTING">said</EVENT> he was not keen on the big money on offer in the Chinese Super League. 
 
China, no. I am not interested. I <EVENT eid="e27" class="I_STATE">dont think</EVENT> about that, not for one moment. My football is here. My heart is here. I <EVENT eid="e28" class="I_STATE">dont think</EVENT> about any other club. Not at all, he <EVENT eid="e29" class="REPORTING">said</EVENT>. 
 
